            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>chicken breast portion[s] </strong>to a clean chopping board</p><p>Slice through the thickest part of the chicken breast, being careful not to cut all the way through to the other side and open it out like a book</p><p>Cover with<strong> cling film</strong> and bash with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> until you have an even thickness – this is your <strong>butterflied chicken</strong></p><p>Add 3 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [4 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [6 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> to a plate and season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1681900692613-x200.jpg",
