            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Coat the <strong>butterflied chicken</strong> in the flour, pressing firmly to coat them evenly</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once very hot, add the<strong> coated chicken</strong> and cook for 4 min on each side or until golden, then turn the heat down to medium and add a knob of <strong>butter </strong>and cook for a further 3-4 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
